FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Got questions about our mobile development app? We've got answers!
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What platforms does your app support?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app supports both iOS and Android platforms, allowing you to develop cross-platform mobile applications efficiently.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Do I need prior coding experience to use this app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: While coding experience is beneficial, our app is designed with user-friendly interfaces and drag-and-drop features, making it accessible for beginners and experts alike.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I create native apps using your platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, our app allows you to create both native and hybrid mobile applications, giving you flexibility in your development approach.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Yes, our app allows seamless integration with a wide range of third-party APIs, enhancing the functionality and features of your mobile applications.
